N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 326.3 - Review of case records

State Regulations

Staff of the department will be responsible for the
review of case records and the completion of the quality control review. Local
social services officials shall make available to department staff in a prompt
fashion, all records which pertain to the case, including financial
data. Notes
